{"content": "I'll solve this step-by-step, converting to base 10, multiplying, then converting back to base 9.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n678\u2089 = 6\u00d79\u00b2 + 7\u00d79\u00b9 + 8\u00d79\u2070 = 6\u00d781 + 7\u00d79 + 8\u00d71 = 486 + 63 + 8 = 557\u2081\u2080\n\n286\u2089 = 2\u00d79\u00b2 + 8\u00d79\u00b9 + 6\u00d79\u2070 = 2\u00d781 + 8\u00d79 + 6\u00d71 = 162 + 72 + 6 = 240\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n557 \u00d7 240 = 557 \u00d7 (200 + 40)\n= 557 \u00d7 200 + 557 \u00d7 40\n= 111,400 + 22,280\n= 133,680\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n133,680 \u00f7 9 = 14,853 r 3\n14,853 \u00f7 9 = 1,650 r 3\n1,650 \u00f7 9 = 183 r 3\n183 \u00f7 9 = 20 r 3\n20 \u00f7 9 = 2 r 2\n2 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 2\n\nReading from bottom to top: 223333\u2089\n\n**Step 4: Verification**\n\n223333\u2089 = 2\u00d759049 + 2\u00d76561 + 3\u00d7729 + 3\u00d781 + 3\u00d79 + 3\u00d71\n= 118,098 + 13,122 + 2,187 + 243 + 27 + 3\n= 133,680\u2081\u2080 \u2713\n\n**223333**", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1245, "completion_tokens": 480}